  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>To characterize the PK profile of adefovir 0.14 mg/kg and 0.3 mg/kg in children 2-11 years, including dose proportionality of adefovir dipivoxil liquid formulation. To characterize the PK profile of adefovir dipivoxil 10 mg in adoloscents 12-17 years.</measure>
    <time_frame>8 days</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
